%F A396373 Equals (1/5) * exp(455/432 - zeta'(-5)/30 - 2*zeta'(-3) - 149*zeta'(-1)/30).
%F A396373 Equals (1/5) * exp(303733/453600 + 751*(gamma + log(2*Pi))/1890 - 149*zeta'(2)/(60*Pi^2) + 3*zeta'(4)/(2*Pi^4) - zeta'(6)/(8*Pi^6)), where gamma is Euler's constant (A001620).
%F A396373 Equals (1/5) * exp(1381/2160 - 2*zeta'(-3) - zeta'(-5)/30) * A^(149/30), where A is the Glaisher-Kinkelin constant (A074962).
